The band The Tap Tap, together with other performers, has also recorded the so-called Anthem against the End of the World titled "The End of the World".
Already today, the anthem is very popular on YouTube. Will it also sound at the charity concerts?
Of course, and at the end of the day, assuming everything works and the end of the world does not happen...
The anthem is to be sung by all the performers at all three concerts at the same time.
